Package: CloudBurglar
Type: Package
Title: Load or Download SharePoint and OneDrive Files by URL
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    "Mike", "McMahon",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "Mike.McMahon@dfo-mpo.gc.ca",
    comment = NULL
  )
Description: Provides a single function to load files from 
  Microsoft SharePoint or OneDrive directly into R using just a sharing link 
  URL. Supports seamless loading of CSV, TSV, Excel, TXT, RDS, and RData files 
  into your workspace, with all other file types downloaded automatically to 
  your working directory. Avoids manual navigation and download steps, making it 
  easier to access files from Office365 sharing links.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
  Microsoft365R,
  readr,
  stringr
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Config/testthat/edition: 3
